reviewText: I use to have this VHS tape as a kid. Id watch it so much it eventually warped and would work anymore. This episode was amazing I remember some of the previews too. Like the Wheres Waldo spaghettios and I believe a Pepsi Commercial That has Mcully Kulkin in it.

Dude, this cartoon is amazing. The Wheres Waldo cartoon may never get released on dvd but atleast I can enjoy it still while there are awesome sellers out there on amazon. If you've never seen this cartoon and grew up in the 80's or 90's, it's well worth your time to check it out.
